snippet.title: {Undefined} Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
{Undefined} is a sandbox survival game, set on life-sized voxel planets with realistic phyisics with the possibility to shape your own building blocks. From your custom made furniture, walls to vehicle parts. You shape the blocks which can then be used to build buildings, spacecraft and aircraft.

Early Access available NOW on Steam! Add it to your wishlist now!
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1548130/Undefined

Website: https://undefinedthegame.com
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/undefinedTheGame
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/undefinedthegame
